00:21:06.520 --> 00:21:07.560
Masuk.

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:10.920
Saaransh, Roohi..
Apa yang kamu lakukan disini?

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:12.440
Tuan memanggil kami berdua ke sini.

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:16.080
